snippet.title: Gameplay Preview Trailer | Warcraft Arclight Rumble
snippet.description:
Introducing Warcraft Arclight Rumble! 

Six game modes, 70+ maps, over 60 collectible characters, and a whole world of joyful chaos to experience. 

Pre-register today: http://warcraftrumble.blizzard.com 
#WarcraftRumble

Follow us on social!
Instagram: http://instagram.com/warcraftrumble
Facebook: http://facebook.com/warcraftrumble
Twitter: http://twitter.com/warcraftrumble
Twitch: http://twitch.tv/warcraftrumble

Stay up to date on all things Warcraft Arclight Rumble here: http://warcraftrumble.blizzard.com
